                <h1>From reliever to middle of the order slugger: Tracing back Duke baseball&#039;s Matt Mervis&#039; journey</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/7663b2fe-3f39-42de-a26d-30bdf959a29a.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="Matt&#x20;Mervis&#x20;has&#x20;been&#x20;a&#x20;power&#x20;threat&#x20;from&#x20;the&#x20;left&#x20;side&#x20;this&#x20;season." class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            Matt Mervis has been a power threat from the left side this season.

