                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>"In high school it was probably one of the things we had to work on more than anything was Matt would beat himself up. I think learning and maturing to manage that has been a big change in his game. You fast forward into college and you have to sit a lot more than you ever have, that’s not always easy for guys. I think that really tested him so I’m glad he’s worked through that and I think it’s really starting to pay off.”</p>
